product.title: Cafe Escapes Coffee
product.description: Coffee is a brewed drink prepared from roasted coffee beans, the seeds of berries from certain Coffea species. ... Coffee is darkly colored, bitter, slightly acidic and has a stimulating effect in humans, primarily due to its caffeine content.
